  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotels popular <strong>ARC Restaurant</strong> has<span> sweeping harbour views and a hyper-local "plant to plate" philosophy. Its a perfect and convenient option for casual and refined dining in downtown Vancouver. </span></p>
<p><span>This Fairmont Waterfront is offered on a room only board, giving you the flexibility and choice to explore the local area and all the fantastic restaurants. </span></p>
<p><span>If you prefer to dine in-house that's not a problem and can be arranged locally - kids aged 5 and under eat free.</span></p>
<p><span>If you want a lazy night in, the 24/7 In-room dining option is a must! You can dine in comfort and enjoy the views from your room. </span></p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>Right on the waters edge of Vancouver Harbour, the Fairmont Waterfront is conveniently located in downtown <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/29418ba1ab4e4c3a81028c3e46a803ff" href="/{localLink:umb://document/29418ba1ab4e4c3a81028c3e46a803ff}" target="_blank" title="Vancouver">Vancouver</a> close to historic Gastown, Chinatown and Stanley Park making it a perfect base to explore the city.</p>
<h2>Excellent Service</h2>
<p>Expect first class service and a wide range of amenities. You'll enjoy the great views over the city and Harbour, many of which are are showcased from the guest rooms. The outdoor rooftop <span>heated swimming pool is open year round and has some pretty nice views too.</span></p>
<h2><span>Dining</span></h2>
<p>The popular ARC Restaurant and bar is casual yet refined and offers a convenient place to relax and dine. Many dishes are influenced by local produce and <span>herbs grown from the 2,100 square foot rooftop garden.</span><span></span></p>]]></description>
